<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1078702" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Clarissimo at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Pereximio 
                        <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petro Antonio Michelotti</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Johannes Bernoulli</rs></salute></opener>
<p>Putabam ego omnia esse confecta nihil<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> superesse quam
                        <lb/>ut solennes Litter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Vocationis mitteren<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>; sed nunc demum non
                        <lb/>sine aliquo stupore intelligo ex novissimis Tuis, Vir
                        <lb/>doctissime, <rs key="B_991170515019405501" type="letter">Litteris</rs>, h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sitari in Valore Thaleri; Nosti ser<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>monem semper fuisse de Thaleris uncialibus non de illis qui
                        <lb/>sesquifloreno germanico singuli <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quivalent: Et Tu quo<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Vir
                        <lb/><choice><abbr>Clariss.</abbr><expan>Clarissime</expan></choice> in Litteris Tuis pleris<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> non aliter de 1500 thaleris
                        <lb/>Imperialibus loquebaris quam de totidem unciis argenti; qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ihat">î</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>
                        <lb/>fit igitur, quod res ista de novo mihi proponatur tanquam
                        <lb/>dubia et incerta; nolim profecto ita ex animi sententia
                        <lb/>loquor, deteriorem expectare conditionem, quam cujus
                        <lb/>mihi spem fecisti, sed omnia potius in irritum relabi
                        <lb/>sinam, nam in eo vel maxime honorem meum versari pu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>to, ut non viliori jam habear pretio quam fuerat pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>missum: Cogita qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so de ante actis; scis me nunquam
                        <lb/>ambivisse <rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavinam</rs>, quinimo diu multum<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
                        <lb/>vestris compellationibus restitisse, antequam innumeris
                        <lb/>assultibus victus consensum darem; quem tandem
                        <pb facs="1078703" n="2"/>
<lb/>dedi extortum magis quam spontaneum, potius<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> mehercle
                        <lb/>eum in finem ut vestro quam meo satisfacerem desiderio
                        <lb/>meisve commodis velificarer. At vero me nunc liberum <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> da<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ta fide censere possem, nisi rationem haberem impensissimi
                        <lb/>Tui erga me amoris et magnorum quos memoras M<choice><orig><g ref="#oe">œ</g></orig><reg>oe</reg></choice>cenatum
                        <lb/>benevolenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ob quam lubens patiar, ut semel adhuc
                        <lb/>tentes an obtinere possis promissum salarium 1500
                        <lb/>thalerorum uncialium, vel, quod eodem circiter recidit,
                        <lb/>quadringentorum Ludovicorum aureorum Gallis Louis d’or <!-- zweite Muenzart, in der besagter Lohn ausbezahlt werden kann -->
<lb/>dictorum, ita nam<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> nulla ambiguitas supererit, siquid<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
                        <lb/>hanc monetam etiam apud Vos in usu esse sciam.
                        <lb/>Non est, quod multis me moneas, tantum stipendium
                        <lb/>esse extraordinarium et insuet<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> magnitudinis,
                        <lb/>quo Viri etiam me long<choice><orig><g ref="#eacut">é</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> superiores et digniores non
                        <lb/>gavisi sunt, sed rationes Tibi exposui in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cedentib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice>
                        <lb/>meis epistolis (Tibi ut videba<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice> non improbatas) ob
                        <lb/>quas minori su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a permoveri non poteram, postquam
                        <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim recusassem multoties Batavorum invitatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nes<note type="editorial">Johann I Bernoulli wurde im August 1703 als Professor der Philosophie und Mathematik an die Universität Utrecht berufen. Im September 1705 folgte eine erneute Einladung durch deren Rektor Burman. Ebenso wurde er im August 1705 nach Leyden berufen, eine erneute Einladung folgte im Mai 1709.</note> cum annexis conditionibus non minus lautis et
                        <lb/>honorificis, quam aliunde unquam vel sperare
                        <lb/>vel expectare possem. Quod attinet ad tempus
                        <pb facs="1078704" n="3"/>
<lb/>in quod me adstringere deberem, si res ista successum
                        <lb/>tandem sortiatur, rationes adsunt et vobis et mihi valitur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                        <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pro triennio militant potius quam pro sexennio; nam
                        <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terquam quod <rs type="organisation">Magistratus</rs> nostri haud <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gre quidem in
                        <lb/>tres annos se difficulter in sex annos sint consensuri, ne<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
                        <lb/>ego pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>videre possim an res me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> domestic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tam long<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
                        <lb/>absentiam mihi permittant, hoc insuper ab <choice><abbr>Ampliss.</abbr><expan>Amplissimis</expan></choice>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Proceribus</rs> vestris considerandum, quod si forte expectationi de
                        <lb/>me concept<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> non essem satisfacturus, haberent san<choice><orig><g ref="#eacut">é</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> duplo
                        <lb/>majorem dolendi causam si me in sexennium conduxissent
                        <lb/>quam tantum in triennium: Hoc vero elapso, et si nihil
                        <lb/>tunc impedierit diuturniorem meam in oris vestris co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>oration<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>,
                        <lb/>prolongari poterit terminus impetrata venia de novo <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="organisation">Magis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tratu</rs> nostro, quod facilius fiet, quam si una vice sex<supplied> </supplied>anni peteren<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tur: Idem etiam cense de nostro <rs type="organisation">senatu academico</rs>, qui ut pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>vi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>deo non quidem graviter feret absentiam meam triennialem,
                        <lb/>sed de venia sexennali ab eo obtinenda statim spondere non
                        <lb/>ausim. En habes Vir <choice><abbr>Clariss.</abbr><expan>Clarissime</expan></choice> sinceram mentis me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> explicati<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>onem, utere jam ea prout <choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> re esse videbitur, me<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> interim
                        <lb/>amare perge.</p> <closer><salute>Vale.</salute><dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1714-10-20">XX<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> <choice><abbr>octobr.is</abbr><expan>octobris</expan></choice> 1714.</date></dateline></closer>
<postscript><p>P. S. Si <rs key="biblio_69NKSR46 biblio_W6BHQDM2 biblio_BS83R2A4 biblio_RTB4565Q" type="biblio">Librorum fasciculus</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Nobis Tibi transmissus nondum
          <lb/>ad manus Tuas pervenit, perveniet, ut spero propediem;
          <lb/>nam diu satis jam in itinere existit.<note type="editorial">Am Ende des letzten Briefes vom 05.10.1714 erwähnt Michelotti, dass er das von Nicolaus I Bernoulli versandte Bündel noch nicht erhalten hat.</note></p></postscript>
